  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Gavl</title>

    <para>
      <application>Gavl</application> is short for Gmerlin Audio Video Library.
It is a low level library that handles the details of audio and video
formats like colorspaces, samplerates, multichannel configurations etc. It
provides standardized definitions for those formats as well as container
structures for carrying audio samples or video images inside an application.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

